title: DAZ3D - Cyberpunk City
description:
Cyberpunk city is a mixture of neoclassical and industrial architecture fused with sci fi noir elements. Billboards, neon and mixed language signage litter this desolate city street along with numerous shop windows and residential apartments. Each building is separated for camera access and both Iray & 3dLight shaders are supplied. Atlas textures are provided for performance and the scene is fully enclosed with hideable walls.
